{"title":"ABAP: Sintaxe","uid":"7dfad76e64f44c07b3d1c07e4d7f0901","slug":"abap-02-syntax","date":"2022-11-06T17:27:00.163Z","updated":"2022-11-06T17:32:22.109Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/abap-02-syntax.json","keywords":["SAP","ABAP","Learn","Aprender","Software","Programação","Desenvolvimento","Desenvolvimento de Software"],"cover":"/img/default-cover.png","content":"<p>O ABAP possui uma sintaxe bastante baseada em palavras-chave como outras linguagens de sua geração (FORTRAN, COBOL, SQL, C++, …), mas também possui uma sintaxe baseada em expressões, operadores e funções pré definidas como em linguagens mais modernas devido à sua evolução. Ambos os estilos são interoperaveis uma vez que a linguagem principal não quebra a retro compatibilidade.</p>\n<h3 id=\"Sintaxe-Basica\"><a href=\"#Sintaxe-Basica\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Sintaxe Básica\"></a>Sintaxe Básica</h3><p><code>&lt;PALAVRA-CHAVE&gt;</code> <code>&lt;ADITIVOS&gt;</code> <code>&lt;FIM INSTRUÇÃO&gt;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> hello <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Olá'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> world <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Mundo!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WRITE</span> hello <span class=\"token string-operator keyword\">&amp;&amp;</span> world<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Principais Caracteristicas de uma Instrução ABAP:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Não possuem distinção entre espaçamentos extras, quebra de linha ou identação.</li>\n<li>Declarações não possuem distinção entre maiusculas&#x2F;minusculas <em>Case Insesitive</em></li>\n<li>Normalmente começam com uma palavra chave <em>ABAP Keyword</em></li>\n<li>Devem possuir pelo menos um espaço entre palavras.</li>\n<li>Devem ser encerradas com um ponto <code>.</code> <em>End Statement</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Instrucoes-Encadeadas\"><a href=\"#Instrucoes-Encadeadas\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Instruções Encadeadas\"></a>Instruções Encadeadas</h3><p><code>&lt;PALAVRA-CHAVE&gt;</code> <code>&lt;OPERADOR&gt;</code><br>        <code>&lt;INSTRUÇÃO 1&gt;</code> <code>&lt;SEPARADOR&gt;</code><br>        <code>&lt;INSTRUÇÃO N&gt;</code> <code>&lt;SEPARADOR&gt;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    hello <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Olá'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    world <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Mundo!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WRITE</span> hello <span class=\"token string-operator keyword\">&amp;&amp;</span> world<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Instruções consecutivas podem ser combinadas através do operador de encadeamento após a palavra chave inicial <code>:</code> <em>Chain Operator</em> e separadas entre cada repetição por virgula <code>,</code> <em>Comma Separator</em></p>\n<p>Chamamos essa combinação de instruções encadeadas <em>Chained Statements</em></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Comentarios\"><a href=\"#Comentarios\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Comentários\"></a>Comentários</h3><p><code>*</code> <code>&quot;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Programa: RESERVAS</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Autor: ABAP Developer</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPORT</span> BOOKINGS<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* Recupera os dados das reservas de hospedagem do banco de dados</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> booking_info\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> accommodation_type <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'S'</span>          <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" Reservas em Suites</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> check_in_date     <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> sy_datum<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>    <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" A partir da data atual</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Comentarios podem ser declarados de duas formas: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Asterisco <code>*</code> como primeiro caractere de uma linha</li>\n<li>Aspas duplas <code>&quot;</code> em qualquer parte do código</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Qualquer declaração após estes caracteres, na mesma linha, serão consideradas comentários e não serão interpretadas pelo compilador</p>\n<h3 id=\"Exemplo-de-Representacao-Sintatica\"><a href=\"#Exemplo-de-Representacao-Sintatica\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Exemplo de Representação Sintática\"></a>Exemplo de Representação Sintática</h3><p>Para facilizar a visualização dos conceitos relacionados à sintaxe, previamente apresentados, segue o código de um programa em ABAP junto a sua representação sintática.</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Neste exemplo, para suprimir espaço e facilitar a visualização, iremos: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chamar todos os identificadores de <em>Name</em> </li>\n<li>Chamar todos os valores literais de <em>Value</em></li>\n<li>Chamar todas os principais operadores de <em>Operator</em></li>\n<li>Chamar todas as palavras-chave de <em>Keywords</em></li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li><em>Identificadores</em> são nomes atribuidos aos dados declarados (ex: variaveis, funções, …)</li>\n<li><em>Valores Literais</em> são valores estáticos que expressam a sí, de forma literal, no código</li>\n<li><em>Palavras-chaves</em> representam recusos da linguagem em forma de comandos</li>\n<li><em>Operadores</em> são um tipo de <em>aditivo</em> para manipulação de dados</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<table width=100%>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Código ABAP</th>\n<th>Representação Sintática</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Report Z_REPORT_ALV_01</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPORT</span> z_report_alv_01<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Declaração dos dados</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">TABLES</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> spfli<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">TYPES</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n  <span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OF</span> ty_spfli<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    airpfrom  <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>airpfrom<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    countryfr <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>countryfr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    cityfrom  <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>cityfrom<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    airpto    <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>airpto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    countryto <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>countryto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    cityto    <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>cityto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">END</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OF</span> ty_spfli<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  lt_spfli <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TABLE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OF</span> ty_spfli<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  lo_alv <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">REF</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TO</span> cl_salv_table<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Declaração dos parâmetros da tela</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECTION-SCREEN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OF</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">BLOCK</span> block01 \n  <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FRAME</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TITLE</span> TEXT<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>t01<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT-OPTIONS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      s_carrid <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>carrid<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      s_connid <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>connid<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      s_fltime <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>fltime<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      s_dtime  <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>deptime<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      s_atime  <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>arrtime<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      s_dist   <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> spfli<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>distance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECTION-SCREEN</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">END</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OF</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">BLOCK</span> block01<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Seleção dos Dados</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span>\n  airpfrom\n  countryfr\n  cityfrom\n  airpto\n  countryto\n  cityto\n<span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> spfli\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TABLE</span> lt_spfli\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> carrid    <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_carrid\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> connid    <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_connid\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> fltime    <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_fltime\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> deptime   <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_dtime\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> arrtime   <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_atime\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">distance</span>  <span class=\"token keyword\">IN</span> s_dist<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">IF</span> sy<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>subrc <span class=\"token keyword\">NE</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">MESSAGE</span> TEXT<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-</span>e01 <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'E'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">LEAVE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">LIST-PROCESSING</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ENDIF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Exibição dos Dados</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------ *</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">TRY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n    cl_salv_table<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">=></span>factory<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> \n      <span class=\"token keyword\">IMPORTING</span> \n        r_salv_table <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> lo_alv\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">CHANGING</span>  \n        t_table      <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> lt_spfli <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n    lo_alv<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-></span>get_functions<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>->set_all<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n    lo_alv<span class=\"token token-operator punctuation\">-></span>display<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">CATCH</span> cx_salv_msg<span 